name: Good Morning Paradise
description:
The quality of lives in favelas in 2070 has risen after the advent of cheap solar energy, and the revamp of the sewer systems. But the worker classes still have a shadow over them: the complete loss of privacy due to the omniscient mega companies who own your 24h contracts.



Oploaded for oBRjkt2

2160 x 3840 3D Rendered PNG. Blender, Substance Designer and coffee
